snippet.title: WITCH CRY 2 OFFICIAL TRAILER 🐺
snippet.description:
Timmy left the witch's house and with the help of Gretel he will try and escape from this fantasy-like but horrifying world! Will you be able to follow her instructions and get the red cape?

WITCH CRY 2 🐺
🔸Google Play: https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.honigames.witchcry2 
🔹App Store: https://apps.apple.com/app/witch-cry-2-the-red-hood/id6475814489
